---------------------

-- LC3 --
this is my slightly modified version of LC3



-----[REGISTERS]-----

x - GP 8bit register
y - GP 8bit register
z - GP 8bit register
w - GP 8bit register
a - GP 8bit register
b - GP 8bit register
c - GP
d - GP

PC - Program Counter

COND - Flags


------[INSTRUCTIONS]-----
0 ADD   - Add
1 LD    - Load
2 ST    - Store
3 JSR   - jump register
4 AND   - Bitwise and
5 LDR   - Load Register
6 STR   - Store Register
7 RTI   - unused
8 NOT   - Bitwise NOT
9 LDI   - load indirect
10 STI   - Store indirect
11 JMP   - jump
12 RES   - reserved unused
13 LEA   - load effective address
14 TRAP  - execute trap

